{"tid":1932664,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有人因班機延誤凌晨抵港成首批強制檢疫者　稱感到無奈","createTime":"2020-03-19T00:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T08:19:41.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4701bb3733346a60dc3ec0df6eea945ffe85ffbc","tid":1932664,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:40:32.000Z","msg":"外國地區到港人士強制檢疫14日的措施，凌晨起實施，為期3個月。一班原定昨晚9時左右，由澳洲墨爾本抵港的航班，延遲至凌晨約3時半抵港，乘客成為首批接受強制檢疫的人，部分人出閘時不單止戴上口罩，更穿著雨衣。<br />\n<br />\n乘客黃先生說，已專登更改機票提早回港，希望趕及在新措施生效前回港，對於航班延誤導致要家居隔離，感到無奈，又說機組人員有盡力解答乘客對於隔離安排的問題，認為講解清晰。<br />\n<br />\n另一名乘客羅先生就形容自己「心情好曳」，又說起飛前在機上等待，已很無奈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515408-20200319.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515408-20200319.htm&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=c39448f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515408-20200319.htm&h=44e60327\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515408-20200319.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ef6954f78aa42c794fe25b508531b58afc1a868b","tid":1932664,"uid":214997,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:45:42.000Z","msg":"姐係本身無撚諗住隔離啦屌"},{"pid":"e9c5eee9aaf1d113bea40ff0a17266b7d7d60ac7","tid":1932664,"uid":34140,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:46:40.000Z","msg":"死撚哂佢啦成班自私精"},{"pid":"40ac80969b7c32781d012570abcd22cd89e92ab7","tid":1932664,"uid":252593,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:48:18.000Z","msg":"睇到火都撚晒<br />\n咁無恥唔想隔離建議免費送返佢地返出發地<br />\n真係死都唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"e55ef7a51cf5dc5ca77d07fafbbaa2cb06c4696f","tid":1932664,"uid":68215,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DoxSpiV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDoxSpiV.jpg&